DarkMouse::
She smiled up at KitKat. "So, you want to get something to eat? After all 
you've been through, I'm sure your starved."

KitKat2::
"Yes, I am a bit hungry. Thank you DarkMouse. You always were a good 
friend."

DarkMouse led KitKat to the cafateria and got them both something to eat.  
After the small meal, KitKat looked at DarkMouse.

::KitKat2::
"You still haven't told me how Drillbit is doing. Is he still alright?"

::DarkMouse::
"Well, I put a call into him, but he hasn't responded to the commlink.  But 
he's around here somewhere."

::KitKat2::
She opened her commlink. "Drillbit. It's me, KitKat. I need to talk to you. 
Please respond."
